Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" IN ('Any Covenanted Payment', 'Direct Debit', 'Standing Order') THEN CASE WHEN "%2" = 'Monthly' THEN "%3" * 12 WHEN "%2" = 'Quarterly' THEN "%3" * 4 WHEN "%2" = 'Half Yearly' THEN "%3" * 2 ELSE "%3" END ELSE 0 END
